item.title: SoftLayer_Provisioning_Version1_Transaction_Group
item.description: SoftLayer_Provisioning_Version1_Transaction_Group Service Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Provisioning_Version1_Transaction_Group data type contains general information relating to a single SoftLayer hardware transaction group. SoftLayer customers are unable to change their hardware transactions or the hardware transaction group. Local averageTimeToComplete Average time, in minutes, for this type of transaction to complete. Please note that this is only an estimate. Type: decimal name A transaction group's name. Type: string
